{
  "video_id": "h815ocHjbwI",
  "title": "Meet Nintendo's Original Gaming Master",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 664.0,
      "end_time": 3400.0,
      "text": "(upbeat music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3400.0,
      "end_time": 5390.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Finding the master sword in Zelda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 9500.0,
      "end_time": 11193.0,
      "text": "bouncing on a Goomba in Mario,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 12320.0,
      "end_time": 14380.0,
      "text": "honing your skills in a duck hunt."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 14380.0,
      "end_time": 15960.0,
      "text": "All things you probably did"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15960.0,
      "end_time": 19100.0,
      "text": "as a kid with your first Nintendo system."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19100.0,
      "end_time": 22650.0,
      "text": "For most of us, playing games was a pastime."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22650.0,
      "end_time": 25372.0,
      "text": "But for one lucky man, this wasn't some hobby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26270.0,
      "end_time": 27393.0,
      "text": "it was his job."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37576.0,
      "end_time": 40326.0,
      "text": "1981 was a year of new frontiers."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42730.0,
      "end_time": 45769.0,
      "text": "In the U.S., a new decade of technology and pop culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45770.0,
      "end_time": 48600.0,
      "text": "was approaching, making it a promising land"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48600.0,
      "end_time": 50530.0,
      "text": "for booming Japanese companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51210.0,
      "end_time": 54710.0,
      "text": "America had said hello to a kitty a few years earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54710.0,
      "end_time": 56860.0,
      "text": "but it was a gorilla that stole the attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56860.0,
      "end_time": 58133.0,
      "text": "of the new generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59200.0,
      "end_time": 62230.0,
      "text": "Donkey Kong was Nintendo's first big breakthrough"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62230.0,
      "end_time": 64539.0,
      "text": "in the western arcade scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64540.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67000.0,
      "text": "The game helped the Japanese company climb its way"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67000.0,
      "end_time": 70180.0,
      "text": "up to America, eventually establishing a new headquarter"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70180.0,
      "end_time": 72893.0,
      "text": "in Seattle, Washington, to bolster their hit."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74370.0,
      "end_time": 77390.0,
      "text": "This is the story of one of their first employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77390.0,
      "end_time": 80223.0,
      "text": "who was soon to become a gaming legend."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82210.0,
      "end_time": 83420.0,
      "text": "- No!"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85110.0,
      "end_time": 87160.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] This is Howard Phillips."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87160.0,
      "end_time": 89160.0,
      "text": "This is Howard Phillips' gaming jacket."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89160.0,
      "end_time": 93520.0,
      "text": "This is Howard Phillips' original 1989 Game Boy"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93520.0,
      "end_time": 96259.0,
      "text": "and this is how Howard started working at Nintendo."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 97410.0,
      "text": "- Kind of embarrassing."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98490.0,
      "end_time": 101860.0,
      "text": "I started at Nintendo in 1981."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101860.0,
      "end_time": 104660.0,
      "text": "It was really just the five or six of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104660.0,
      "end_time": 107190.0,
      "text": "I was the shipping warehouse manager."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107190.0,
      "end_time": 110380.0,
      "text": "My role was to bring in all of the arcade games"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110380.0,
      "end_time": 112740.0,
      "text": "and unload them and record all the serial numbers"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112740.0,
      "end_time": 114780.0,
      "text": "and then pack them up for shipment."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 114780.0,
      "end_time": 115700.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] It doesn't sound"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115700.0,
      "end_time": 117470.0,
      "text": "like the greatest gig in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117470.0,
      "end_time": 120850.0,
      "text": "but working in the warehouse came with one pretty big perk."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120850.0,
      "end_time": 123429.0,
      "text": "- [Howard] I could play all the games."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 123430.0,
      "end_time": 125560.0,
      "text": "Whenever a new game came in, I could open it up"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 125560.0,
      "end_time": 126950.0,
      "text": "and plug it in and play it."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 126950.0,
      "end_time": 128289.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] But playing games could never"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 128288.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131350.0,
      "text": "be a full-time career, or could it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131350.0,
      "end_time": 133987.0,
      "text": "Nintendo of America was run by this man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 133987.0,
      "end_time": 135463.0,
      "text": "Mr. Minoru Arakawa."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 136680.0,
      "end_time": 139340.0,
      "text": "The company was looking to break into the U.S. market"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139340.0,
      "end_time": 141620.0,
      "text": "but needed a little advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 141620.0,
      "end_time": 145350.0,
      "text": "- The Japanese are very, very attentive to the customer"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145350.0,
      "end_time": 147170.0,
      "text": "and the customer was king."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147170.0,
      "end_time": 150400.0,
      "text": "I was their, kind of, gateway  into the U.S. zeitgeist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150400.0,
      "end_time": 153230.0,
      "text": "I used to know what players really wanted to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154220.0,
      "end_time": 155540.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Why you, Howard?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155540.0,
      "end_time": 158690.0,
      "text": "- Who knows why out of the few people working"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158690.0,
      "end_time": 160990.0,
      "text": "in the company at the time that I got selected"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 160990.0,
      "end_time": 164560.0,
      "text": "as being one of the more true voices."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 164560.0,
      "end_time": 167460.0,
      "text": "I think it was just my enthusiasm for play."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 167460.0,
      "end_time": 169950.0,
      "text": "You know, I’m a player's player, I love to play games."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 169950.0,
      "end_time": 171399.0,
      "text": "I love to play at everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 172591.0,
      "end_time": 175140.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] In 1985, Nintendo was ready to move"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 175140.0,
      "end_time": 177480.0,
      "text": "out from the arcade and into the living room."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 177480.0,
      "end_time": 178890.0,
      "text": "- Mr. Arakawa said to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178890.0,
      "end_time": 180880.0,
      "text": "“What do you think are the best games?”"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 180880.0,
      "end_time": 182420.0,
      "text": "I played them all, and I said, “Mr. Arakawa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 182420.0,
      "end_time": 184320.0,
      "text": "these are the best 15 games.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 184320.0,
      "end_time": 186870.0,
      "text": "“Everybody will love these games.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 186870.0,
      "end_time": 189520.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] And so the game master was born."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 189520.0,
      "end_time": 192600.0,
      "text": "- Howard Phillips, also known as Mr. Nintendo."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 192600.0,
      "end_time": 196540.0,
      "text": "It's his job to test every Nintendo game that comes out."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 196540.0,
      "end_time": 197760.0,
      "text": "- What is a game master?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 197760.0,
      "end_time": 202100.0,
      "text": "It was really just a focus on what it means"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 202100.0,
      "end_time": 205100.0,
      "text": "when a player meets a game, it's that connection."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 205100.0,
      "end_time": 206460.0,
      "text": "- We were really looking for someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 206460.0,
      "end_time": 208430.0,
      "text": "to represent the gamer"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 208430.0,
      "end_time": 210890.0,
      "text": "and to speak directly to the gamer."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 210890.0,
      "end_time": 212700.0,
      "text": "And Howard really fit the bill."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 212700.0,
      "end_time": 215250.0,
      "text": "He was like a grownup, but he was still like a kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 216238.0,
      "end_time": 218460.0,
      "text": "He gave you the impression more of a character"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 218460.0,
      "end_time": 219923.0,
      "text": "than a business person."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 220900.0,
      "end_time": 223510.0,
      "text": "- [Howard] I think the connection that I had with players"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 223510.0,
      "end_time": 225773.0,
      "text": "was that shared love of just gaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 227150.0,
      "end_time": 228790.0,
      "text": "And then their mom or dad would show up"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 228790.0,
      "end_time": 231510.0,
      "text": "and they would say, but they're not educational"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 231510.0,
      "end_time": 234709.0,
      "text": "or whatever the negative association was that they wanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 234710.0,
      "end_time": 237270.0,
      "text": "to put with video games and their child."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 237270.0,
      "end_time": 239990.0,
      "text": "- It may be the most addictive toy in history:"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 239990.0,
      "end_time": 241950.0,
      "text": "Nintendo video games."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 241950.0,
      "end_time": 244109.0,
      "text": "- Is it turning their brains to mush?"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 244110.0,
      "end_time": 246220.0,
      "text": "- Shame on people that produce that trash,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 246220.0,
      "end_time": 247923.0,
      "text": "it's child abuse, in my judgment."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 249420.0,
      "end_time": 251890.0,
      "text": "- It was saddening to me that"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 251900.0,
      "end_time": 253942.0,
      "text": "that's how parents perceived their kids' joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 253942.0,
      "end_time": 256283.0,
      "text": "as something that was maybe a negative."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 257250.0,
      "end_time": 259730.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Video games had a bad rep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 259730.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261230.00000000003,
      "text": "but Howard could see the positive effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 261230.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263630.0,
      "text": "that the games had on kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 264130.0,
      "end_time": 266920.0,
      "text": "- It was a shared love of the experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 266920.0,
      "end_time": 268800.0,
      "text": "of discovering something new"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 268800.0,
      "end_time": 271180.0,
      "text": "or being really, really frustrated at something"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 271180.0,
      "end_time": 273950.0,
      "text": "but just trying and being patient and persistent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 273950.0,
      "end_time": 275510.0,
      "text": "which is learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 275510.0,
      "end_time": 277510.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] And the players wanted to learn more:"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 277510.0,
      "end_time": 280580.0,
      "text": "more information, more tricks, more tips,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 280580.0,
      "end_time": 283690.0,
      "text": "and the game master was there to deliver."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 283690.0,
      "end_time": 285800.0,
      "text": "- [Announcer] Nintendo Power: your direct connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 285800.0,
      "end_time": 287490.0,
      "text": "to the pros for better play."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 287490.0,
      "end_time": 290300.0,
      "text": "The official magazine of video mastery."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 290300.0,
      "end_time": 291320.0,
      "text": "For ordering information..."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 291320.0,
      "end_time": 294740.0,
      "text": "- [Howard] My role was to make sure that every single bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 294740.0,
      "end_time": 298890.0,
      "text": "of information in that 132 pages each month"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 298890.0,
      "end_time": 301680.0,
      "text": "was accurate and spoke in a way that the players"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 301680.0,
      "end_time": 304680.0,
      "text": "wanted to understand and know about."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 304680.0,
      "end_time": 307340.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] But that wasn't the only role Howard played."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 307340.0,
      "end_time": 308969.0,
      "text": "- When we were setting up all the columns"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 308970.0,
      "end_time": 311130.0,
      "text": "in Nintendo Power, we thought it would be great"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 311130.0,
      "end_time": 313423.0,
      "text": "to include a comic strip."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 314520.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "- [Howard] Howard and Nester is just a cartoon"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 317880.0,
      "text": "that describes a child player"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 317880.0,
      "end_time": 321900.0,
      "text": "who's always trying to get past the next level in a game."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 321900.0,
      "end_time": 324330.0,
      "text": "And Howard is the game master who knows everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 324330.0,
      "end_time": 327289.0,
      "text": "about the games who can provide some tips."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 327290.0,
      "end_time": 328860.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] And Howard is you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 328860.0,
      "end_time": 329693.0,
      "text": "- That's me."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 332300.0,
      "end_time": 334669.0,
      "text": "Dear Howard Phillips, I am 12 years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 334670.0,
      "end_time": 335923.0,
      "text": "and your biggest fan."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 337290.0,
      "end_time": 339197.0,
      "text": "My friends and I read Nintendo Power."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 339197.0,
      "end_time": 341270.0,
      "text": "You're the best in your business."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 341270.0,
      "end_time": 344760.0,
      "text": "Your biggest fan with a capital B, bye."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 344760.0,
      "end_time": 349560.0,
      "text": "The notoriety of being game master really was crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 349560.0,
      "end_time": 352700.0,
      "text": "I would be pumping gas at the gas station,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 352700.0,
      "end_time": 355590.0,
      "text": "I would be buying potato chips at the supermarket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 355590.0,
      "end_time": 358919.0,
      "text": "or I'd be at a movie and kids would come up to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 358920.0,
      "end_time": 360990.0,
      "text": "and their parents would come up to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 360990.0,
      "end_time": 362690.0,
      "text": "and say “Oh, you're the guy.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 362690.0,
      "end_time": 364969.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] The guy who was able to turn his passion"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 364970.0,
      "end_time": 368830.0,
      "text": "for video games into a once in a lifetime opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 368830.0,
      "end_time": 372140.0,
      "text": "So Howard, what was the best part about being game master?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 372140.0,
